## **Task 3: Environment-Specific Logic**

### Subtask 3.1: Create Mode Detection Script

```bash
# Create advanced entrypoint with environment detection
nano entrypoint.sh
```

**Advanced entrypoint.sh content:**
```bash
#!/bin/bash

echo "ğŸš€ Container Initialization Starting..."
echo "======================================"

# Environment detection with detailed feedback
if [ "$ENV_MODE" = "production" ]; then
    echo "ğŸ­ PRODUCTION MODE ACTIVATED"
    echo "   âœ“ Strict security settings applied"
    echo "   âœ“ Performance optimizations enabled"
    echo "   âœ“ Detailed logging disabled for security"
    echo "   âœ“ Debug features disabled"
    
    # Production-specific environment setup
    export LOG_LEVEL=ERROR
    export DEBUG_MODE=false
    
elif [ "$ENV_MODE" = "development" ]; then
    echo "ğŸ› ï¸  DEVELOPMENT MODE ACTIVATED"
    echo "   âœ“ Debug features enabled"
    echo "   âœ“ Verbose logging activated"
    echo "   âœ“ Hot-reload capabilities enabled"
    echo "   âœ“ Security restrictions relaxed"
    
    # Development-specific environment setup
    export LOG_LEVEL=DEBUG
    export DEBUG_MODE=true
    
elif [ "$ENV_MODE" = "testing" ]; then
    echo "ğŸ§ª TESTING MODE ACTIVATED"
    echo "   âœ“ Test fixtures loaded"
    echo "   âœ“ Mock services enabled"
    echo "   âœ“ Coverage reporting enabled"
    
    # Testing-specific environment setup
    export LOG_LEVEL=INFO
    export DEBUG_MODE=true
    export ENABLE_MOCKS=true
    
else
    echo "âš™ï¸  DEFAULT MODE (No ENV_MODE specified)"
    echo "   âœ“ Standard configuration applied"
    echo "   âœ“ Balanced security and debugging"
    
    # Default environment setup
    export LOG_LEVEL=INFO
    export DEBUG_MODE=false
fi

echo "======================================"
echo "ğŸ“‹ Final Environment Configuration:"
echo "   LOG_LEVEL: $LOG_LEVEL"
echo "   DEBUG_MODE: $DEBUG_MODE"
echo "   ENABLE_MOCKS: ${ENABLE_MOCKS:-false}"
echo "======================================"
echo ""

# Show what command we're about to execute
echo "âš¡ Executing: $@"
echo ""

# Execute the provided command
exec "$@"
```

### Subtask 3.2: Update Containerfile for Environment Variables

```bash
# Update Containerfile with environment support
nano Containerfile
```

**Updated Containerfile:**
```dockerfile
FROM alpine:latest

# Install bash and useful utilities
RUN apk add --no-cache bash coreutils curl

# Set default environment (can be overridden at runtime)
ENV LOG_LEVEL=INFO
ENV DEBUG_MODE=false

# Copy our advanced entrypoint script
COPY entrypoint.sh /entrypoint.sh

# Set the entrypoint and default command
ENTRYPOINT ["/entrypoint.sh"]
CMD ["echo", "Container running with environment:", "$ENV_MODE"]
```

